<% if application.course.senco? %>
  <h3>What if my chosed provider cannot offer me a space on their NPQ course</h3>
  <p class="govuk-!-margin-bottom-2">If you're a SENCO in a maintained school and need to complete the SENCO NPQ in October 2024 but have been told by your provider that you do not have one of the following:</p>

  <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
    <li>
      a space on their course
    </li>
    <li>
      a scholarship funded space on their course
    </li>
  </ul>
  <p class="govuk-body">
    Contact the
    <a href="mailto:continuing-professional-development@digital.education.gov.uk" class="govuk-link">CPD helpdesk</a>
    for support if you have never started or completed the national award for SENCO (NASENCO) qualification before.'
  </p>
<% else %>
  <h3>If no funded place is available</h3>
  <p class="govuk-!-margin-bottom-2">You can:</p>

  <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
    <li>
      register with this provider again later in the year
    </li>
    <li>
      register with a different provider
    </li>
    <li>
      consider other payment options, such as self-funding or asking if your workplace or trust can cover the cost
    </li>
  </ul>
<% end %>
